<doc id="511972" wikidata="Q17026080" url="?curid=511972" title="Money (KMFDM song)">
<text>&quot;Money&quot; is a song by industrial rock group KMFDM from their 1992 album of the same name. It was released as a single in 1992, and released as a 7&quot; in 2008, as the ninth release of KMFDM&#x27;s 24/7 series. The song charted at No. 36 in July 1992 on Billboard&#x27;s Dance/Club Play Songs Chart. The tracks on the single are included on the singles compilation album, &quot;Extra, Vol. 1&quot;.

